<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Proposed Changes for &quot;Summon &lt;item&gt;&quot; Magician Spell Line</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><!--EZCODE LIST START--><ol><li><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Targeted Summons</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->I fully support changing all summon spells to targeted summons.</li><li><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Remove LORE Tag</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->I fully support all summoned items having their LORE tag removed.</li><li><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Remove Recast Time</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->I fully support all summon spells having their recast time removed.</li></ol><!--EZCODE LIST END-->These three factors seem to be there for no other reason than to inconvenience the Magician.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Exceptions to the above rules</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
